949
00:56:36,708 --> 00:56:39,000
<i>Tapi aku merasa, jauh di dalam hati</i>

950
00:56:39,083 --> 00:56:41,333
<i>Di mana bagian aneh diriku bersembunyi</i>

951
00:56:41,416 --> 00:56:44,541
