mungkin tapal?

976
00:59:01,416 --> 00:59:03,541
Atau salep? Itu bisa sangat kuat.

977
00:59:03,625 --> 00:59:05,000
Tak ada salep.

978
00:59:07,666 --> 00:59:09,708
